00:59:01,151 --> 00:59:04,040
Maybe be very careful
writing the KDC code.

1413
00:59:04,040 --> 00:59:06,300
Don't allow you to
log into it directly.

1414
00:59:06,300 --> 00:59:11,060
Maybe you even worry about
